com.musicbox.util.websocket

Class WebsocketTextMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.musicbox.util.websocket.WebsocketTextMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class WebsocketTextMessage
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Messages with Text-Data to send chat-messages or error-messages.
    The websocket-endpoint-server handle chat messages and forwards it to other logged in clients.
    The websocket-endpoint-server sends error messages to clients if an erro occurred.
    Author:
    David Wachs
